race.comment: ADJOURNED (4) ran below his best last time finishing fourth (25.84) over 457m at this track in a Mix 5. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. LARA DUTTON (2) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Filled the minor placings over 457m at this track (25.80) in a Grade 5 but is better placed at the shorter trip here. Strike rate this distance strong having won nine of 16 tries. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Expected to be in the finish again. STAR ASSASSIN (3) is likely to have admirers. Something for the Multiples: SHE'S A LADETTE (8)
